<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Microsoft PowerPoint 2010 (KB2519975), 32-Bit Edition</Title><Description>A security vulnerability exists in Microsoft PowerPoint 2010, 32-Bit Edition that could allow arbitrary code to run when a maliciously modified file is opened. This update resolves that vulnerability.</Description><MoreInfoUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/kb/2519975</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/?LN=en-us</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>